trans-unit.source: Represents a single relationship between an object and a member.
trans-unit.target: 개체와 멤버 사이의 단일 관계를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> is used by a serializer to announce that one property is related to a property on another object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> 직렬 변환기를 통해 하나의 속성이 다른 개체의 속성을 관련 알리는 데 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> represents a single relationship between an object and a member that <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> uses in its interactions with a serializer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> 개체와 멤버 간의 단일 관계를 나타냅니다는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> serializer와의 상호 작용에 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The object that owns <c>member</c>.
The member which is to be related to <c>owner</c>.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> class.
<paramref name="owner" /> or <paramref name="member" /> is <see langword="null" />.
Represents the empty member relationship.
This field is read-only.
A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> structure is empty if neither the owner nor the member is assigned.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> 구조체는 소유자와 멤버가 모두 할당 된 경우 비어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> to compare with the current <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />.
Determines whether two <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> instances are equal.
trans-unit.target: 두 개의 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> 인스턴스가 같은지 여부를 확인합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> is equal to the current <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see langword="true" />가 현재<see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />와 같으면 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> 이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for this instance.
A hash code for the current <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />.
Gets a value indicating whether this relationship is equal to the <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" /> relationship.
trans-unit.target: 이 관계가 <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" /> 관계와 같은지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if this relationship is equal to the <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" /> relationship; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 관계가 <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" /> 관계와 같으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the related member.
The member that is passed in to the <see cref="M:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)" />.
The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the left of the equality operator.
The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the right of the equality operator.
Tests whether two specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are equivalent.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 두 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> 구조체가 동일한지 여부를 테스트합니다.

trans-unit.source: This operator returns <see langword="true" /> if the two <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are equal; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 두 개의 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> 구조체가 동일하면 이 연산자는 <see langword="true" />를 반환하고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the left of the inequality operator.
trans-unit.target: 같지 않음 연산자의 왼쪽에 있는 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> 구조체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the right of the inequality operator.
trans-unit.target: 같지 않음 연산자의 오른쪽에 있는 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> 구조체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Tests whether two specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are different.
trans-unit.target: 두 개의 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> 구조체가 다른지 여부를 테스트합니다.

trans-unit.source: This operator returns <see langword="true" /> if the two <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are different; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 두 개의 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> 구조체가 다르면 이 연산자는 <see langword="true" />를 반환하고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
Gets the owning object.
The owning object that is passed in to the <see cref="M:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)" />.
